{
  "stem": "26699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES] When my mother saw this, we were guarded on the queue by Romanian army officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans, they took only the pleasure to round up the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They left the dirty work to be done by the Romanians themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't want to dirty themselves with blood and-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] Next to us was a young Romanian officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother kneeled in front of him-- she was 28-- [PAUSES] kissed his hand, and asked him, officer, sir, I beg you, take this child and adopt him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's intelligent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He will love you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Please take him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kill us, but take this child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES] The officer said, Madam, [PAUSES] please don't be scared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I'll protect you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And what he did, as the queue was winding, he took us from the position where we were and put us at the end of the queue to give us another chance, to prolong our life.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And this was the second time when my mother saved my life in the same day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Probably this officer was a man who had some sort of conscience, some soul.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He saw a young woman with a little child being exposed to such a terrible death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Our good luck was that this mass execution wasn't organized by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was organized by Romanians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If Germans would have organized this, everything would have gone according to the pogrom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But Romanians are not that precise as the Germans, and probably the ammunition ended, was finished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So until they will bring new ammunition to finish off the people, an order came to let women and children leave the queue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So immediately my mother and I went off that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
